Each of the 4 corner cubes has 4 red faces. Each of the 8 other cubes on the edges has 3 red faces. Each of the 4 central cubes has 2 red faces. Then, each of the corner cubes and each of the central cubes has an even number of red faces. There are $\boxed{8}$ such cubes.

